    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEATH IS A POWER-UP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ancestral Players</strong> reimagines the classic Arena Shooter with a vengeful twist. In this arena, <strong>death is just a power-up.</strong> Every time you fall, you level up, gaining powerful abilities to hunt down the person who just took you out. But remember, your lives are limited: wipe out the competition and be the last man standing.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY FOR FUN OR FOR GLORY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Settle the score with friends in private lobbies or prove your dominance in our regular tournaments.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PRIMITIVE ARSENAL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349430/extras/c8b2675bc4a439ec04ae3c0508c5184b.poster.avif?t=1771675779\" width=750 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349430/extras/c8b2675bc4a439ec04ae3c0508c5184b.webm?t=1771675779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every shot is earned. Master an arsenal where every projectile follows its own path:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Axe:</strong> Heavy, brutal, and deadly at close range.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Bow:</strong> Built for surgical precision at a distance.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Coconut Launcher:</strong> Chaos in a shell. High-impact tropical fruit at its finest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>NO HEROES, JUST BOB</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349430/extras/1988e0aa45a4ca333db3c799f76c79f6.poster.avif?t=1771675779\" width=750 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349430/extras/1988e0aa45a4ca333db3c799f76c79f6.webm?t=1771675779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Ancestral Players, everyone starts on equal footing, equipped with nothing but a dagger and a brief. Depending on the game mode, you will level up either by following a pre-established progression path (inspired by 'gun game' game modes), or pick upgrades yourself in the skill tree game mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349430/extras/b4ed23f674c02701dbe0208e31abea20.poster.avif?t=1771675779\" width=750 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349430/extras/b4ed23f674c02701dbe0208e31abea20.webm?t=1771675779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE ARENA IS ALIVE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349430/extras/8102053e32ad5b77ae86da00573008a4.poster.avif?t=1771675779\" width=750 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349430/extras/8102053e32ad5b77ae86da00573008a4.webm?t=1771675779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players aren’t the only danger in the arena, stay alert to the shifting environment. Master your movements to escape hazardous situations.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-16 players per lobby </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FFA or team mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tournaments (automated in the game)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bots</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Peer2Peer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dedicated servers (Only in Europe/North America)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Split Screen</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LAN </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Replays</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Training Area + Short Solo Campaign </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
